                </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4 text-justify my-auto">
                <p class="photoshoot-title font-weight-bold h3">Lina</p>
                <p class="h4">Donec non erat at quam aliquam pulvinar. Praesent efficitur accumsan hendrerit. Morbi elementum quis eros sit amet molestie. Sed laoreet magna facilisis, volutpat diam et, fringilla nulla. Sed a lectus placerat, aliquam erat eu, lobortis nibh. Pellentesque tristique magna elit, ac cursus turpis ornare et. Nulla congue eros tellus, vitae sollicitudin tortor faucibus non.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4 text-justify my-auto">
                <p class="photoshoot-title font-weight-bold h3">Katya</p>
                <p class="h4">Suspendisse ligula nibh, rhoncus id nisi a, pulvinar consectetur leo. Sed volutpat felis non odio semper, quis varius lectus vulputate. Pellentesque sollicitudin nisi ut sem commodo laoreet. Quisque blandit nec mi sed vulputate. Cras at sem urna. Duis vitae odio mi. Pellentesque ultrices dolor sem. Vestibulum et magna id eros tempus ultrices.</p>

            </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-8 py-4">
                    <!-- Instagram WIDGET -->
                    <!-- LightWidget WIDGET --><script src="https://cdn.lightwidget.com/widgets/lightwidget.js"></script><iframe src="//lightwidget.com/widgets/f19df67f2b7257b7a7046728869b4c49.html" scrolling="no" allowtransparency="true" class="lightwidget-widget" style="width:100%;border:0;overflow:hidden;"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
<section id="contact" class="contact-section text-white text-center">
    <span class="service-icon contact-form-symbol mx-auto">
        <i class="far fa-envelope"></i>
    </span>
    <div class="contactform">
        <span class="content-section-heading text-center">
            <p class="text-dark h2">Drop us a message</p>
        </span>
            {{ form_start(contactForm, {'attr': {'id':'contactForm'} } ) }}
                {{ form_row(contactForm.name) }}
                {{ form_widget(contactForm.email) }}
                {{ form_row(contactForm.text) }}
                 <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg">Send</button>
            {{ form_end(contactForm) }}

        <div class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="contactModal">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <br>
                        <p class="text-dark h3">Thank you!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="send-button" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    <!-- Scroll to Top Button-->
    <a class="scroll-to-top rounded" href="#page-top">
        <i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i>
    </a>
{% endblock %}